Description: Modern NAS Management System
 Stumpf.Works NAS is a production-ready Network Attached Storage management
 system designed as an alternative to TrueNAS, Unraid, and Synology DSM.
 .
 Features:
  - User & Group Management with Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)
  - SMB/CIFS Shares with Samba integration
  - NFS Shares support
  - Docker Container Management (Portainer alternative)
  - SMART Monitoring & Disk Health tracking
  - Storage Management (Volumes, Disks, RAID)
  - File Manager with permissions control
  - Active Directory integration
  - Two-Factor Authentication (2FA)
  - Audit Logging & Security tracking
  - Backup & Snapshot management
  - System Metrics & Health monitoring
  - Automated Task Scheduling
  - Email & Webhook Alerts
  - Plugin System
  - Network Management & Firewall
  - Modern React-based Web UI
 .
 Perfect for home labs, small businesses, and development environments.
